<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
            
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
                        <!-- Getting Started Section -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                                <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                    Getting Started with BenixSpace AI
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <h5>What is BenixSpace AI?</h5>
                                        <p>BenixSpace AI is an innovative platform that uses artificial intelligence to generate professional music tracks from your vocal recordings. Simply record your vocals, and our AI will create matching instrumentals for a complete track.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <h5>How do I get started?</h5>
                                        <p>Getting started with BenixSpace AI is easy:</p>
                                        <ol>
                                            <li>Create a free account</li>
                                            <li>Choose your song structure</li>
                                            <li>Record your vocals for each section</li>
                                            <li>Let our AI generate music based on your vocals</li>
                                            <li>Download or share your completed track</li>
                                        </ol>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5>What equipment do I need?</h5>
                                        <p>All you need is a device with a microphone (computer, smartphone, or tablet) and an internet connection. For better quality recordings, we recommend using a dedicated microphone, but it's not required.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Subscription & Pricing -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                    Subscription & Pricing
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <h5>What subscription plans do you offer?</h5>
                                        <p>We offer three subscription tiers:</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li><strong>Free:</strong> Limited features with basic music generation capabilities</li>
                                            <li><strong>Standard ($9.99/month):</strong> Full music generation features with extended genre options</li>
                                            <li><strong>Professional ($19.99/month):</strong> Advanced features including high-quality exports, extended track length, and commercial usage rights</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <h5>Can I cancel my subscription anytime?</h5>
                                        <p>Yes, you can cancel your subscription at any time. You'll continue to have access to the service until the end of your current billing period.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5>Do you offer a free trial?</h5>
                                        <p>Yes, new users can try our Standard plan free for 7 days. No credit card required for the free trial.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Recording & Music Generation -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                    Recording & Music Generation
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <h5>How does the AI music generation work?</h5>
                                        <p>Our AI analyzes your vocal recordings to determine key, tempo, rhythm, and emotional content. It then creates instrumental accompaniment that perfectly matches your voice and the selected genre.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <h5>What genres are supported?</h5>
                                        <p>We currently support Pop, Rock, Hip Hop, R&B, Electronic, Jazz, and Acoustic genres. We're constantly expanding our genre capabilities.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <h5>Can I edit the generated music?</h5>
                                        <p>Yes, our Professional plan allows you to make basic edits to the generated music, including adjusting instrument levels and applying effects.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5>How long does music generation take?</h5>
                                        <p>Music generation typically takes 1-3 minutes depending on the length of your recording and server load.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Rights & Licensing -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                    Rights & Licensing
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <h5>Who owns the music I create?</h5>
                                        <p>You own the vocal recordings you create. The AI-generated instrumental parts are licensed to you according to your subscription tier:</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Free Plan: Personal use only</li>
                                            <li>Standard Plan: Personal and limited commercial use</li>
                                            <li>Professional Plan: Full commercial rights including monetization</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <h5>Can I use the music commercially?</h5>
                                        <p>Standard and Professional plans allow commercial use of the music you create. The Professional plan offers the most comprehensive commercial rights.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5>Can I upload my music to streaming platforms?</h5>
                                        <p>Yes, Standard and Professional plan subscribers can distribute their music to streaming platforms. Professional plan users receive 100% of streaming royalties.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Technical Support -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                                    Technical Support
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <h5>How can I get technical support?</h5>
                                        <p>You can reach our support team through:</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Email: benirabok@gmail.com</li>
                                            <li>Phone: +250783987223</li>
                                            <li>Help Center: <a href="/help">ai.benix.space/help</a></li>
                                            <li>Contact form: <a href="/contact">ai.benix.space/contact</a></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <h5>What browsers are supported?</h5>
                                        <p>BenixSpace AI works best on Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Edge. We recommend using the latest version of your preferred browser.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5>Is there a mobile app available?</h5>
                                        <p>Currently, we offer a responsive web application that works well on mobile devices. Dedicated iOS and Android apps are coming soon.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card text-center">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4>Still Have Questions?</h4>
                    <p>Our support team is ready to help with any questions you might have.</p>
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Support</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

